# Task dashboard

Tasks live in their project pages. This file surfaces them by category. Do not add tasks here directly. Write them in the relevant project file instead.

## Due in the next 14 days
```tasks
(not done) AND (due before in 14 days) AND (path includes {{wiki_root_basename}}/)
sort by due date
sort by priority
short mode
```

