## All open tasks across {{projects_path}}
```tasks
(not done) AND (path includes {{projects_path}}/)
sort by due date
sort by priority
short mode
```

## Overdue
```tasks
(not done) AND (due before today) AND (path includes {{projects_path}}/)
sort by priority
sort by due
short mode
```

## No due date
```tasks
(not done) AND (no due date) AND (path includes {{projects_path}}/)
sort by priority
short mode
```

## Done today
```tasks
(done today) AND (path includes {{wiki_root_basename}}/)
sort by status
sort by priority
sort by due
short mode
```
